{"tid":1355951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被逼幹不道德或錯誤的事，我會抗命 – 前警務處處長李明逵","createTime":"2019-07-23T11:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:09:59.000Z","uid":4312,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9d9f43fc17ee1fca98be6010d98444daae1b2053","tid":1355951,"uid":4312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:44:28.000Z","msg":"（在回歸後）我們可能要違背自己的意願<br />\n執行我們不想執行的任務<br />\n就以控制人群為例<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>現在我們只需維持法紀及秩序<br />\n九七後或會使用不必要的武力</strong></span><br />\n換句話說<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我們害怕被逼幹違願的事情<br />\n我是本地訓練出來的警官<br />\n當然要站起來說不</strong></span><br />\n（你會違抗命令？）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被逼幹不道德或錯誤的事<br />\n我會抗命</strong></span><br />\n我會留下來直到最後一分鐘<br />\n因為這是我家<br />\n我生於斯長於斯<br />\n是香港把我教育成材<br />\n我要留下來服務香港人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B7Yynbz9M3U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB7Yynbz9M3U&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=27991e4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B7Yynbz9M3U</a>"},{"pid":"27ca91a0dba8788ecec29688a1c2deb35946b1ec","tid":1355951,"uid":4312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:47:20.000Z","msg":"呢家班警察肯醒未"},{"pid":"3111ed429fa95df048fc9c068a812d6f3327d5d1","tid":1355951,"uid":56323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:59:05.000Z","msg":"香港依家冇警察<br />\n只有 有牌爛仔 同無牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0f05e8877b0d473db886f7c31c4a1ebd6fc2ae","tid":1355951,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27ca91a0dba8788ecec29688a1c2deb35946b1ec","tid":1355951,"uid":4312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:47:20.000Z","msg":"呢家班警察肯醒未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:01:25.000Z","msg":"你肯醒未"},{"pid":"e81c16bd20e05daa5967ecfbe4ccf2b87d22d46f","tid":1355951,"uid":27